### Movie Watchlist API — HTTP client requests
@base_url = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Register (saves token)
POST {{base_url}}/api/register
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nikola",
  "email": "nikola@gmail.com",
  "password": "sifra1234!",
  "password_confirmation": "sifra1234!"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

### Login (saves token)
POST {{base_url}}/api/login
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nikola@gmail.com",
  "password": "sifra1234!"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

### Current authenticated user
GET {{base_url}}/api/user
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add a movie by IMDb id (saves the new item id)
POST {{base_url}}/api/watchlist
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "imdb_id": "tt0133093",
  "status": "to_watch",
  "priority": "high",
  "notes": "Recommended by a friend."
}

> {% client.global.set("item_id", response.body.data.id); %}

### Add a movie by title (+ optional year to disambiguate)
POST {{base_url}}/api/watchlist
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Inception",
  "year": 2010,
  "status": "watching"
}

### List the whole watchlist
GET {{base_url}}/api/watchlist
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List with filtering, sorting and pagination
GET {{base_url}}/api/watchlist?status=to_watch&sort=created_at&direction=desc&per_page=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### View a single item
GET {{base_url}}/api/watchlist/{{item_id}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update an item (status -> watched also stamps watched_at)
PATCH {{base_url}}/api/watchlist/{{item_id}}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "watched",
  "rating": 9
}

### Remove an item
DELETE {{base_url}}/api/watchlist/{{item_id}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Log out (revokes the current token)
POST {{base_url}}/api/logout
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
